avos seaworth reveals what souvenir he lifted from the game of thrones set and why this and more in our guide to comiccon watch the video share this page who wore it best at comiccon check out some of our favorite comiccon cosplayers who in some cases looked every bit as good as their inspirations compare cosplayers with their inspirations around the web    powered by zergnet do you have a demo reel add it to your imdbpage find out more at imdb pro » connect with imdb how much have you seen how much of michael ray charless work have you seen known for bamboozled miscellaneous crew  art city  a ruling passion actor  art in the twentyfirst century himself   show all  hide all    show by job year » rating » number of ratings » genre » keyword »    edit filmography jump to miscellaneous crew  thanks  self hide  show  miscellaneous crew  credit   bamboozled paintings bamboozled and mandinis great escape used by kind permission of  visual consultant hide  show  thanks  credit   bamboozled thanks hide  show  self  credits   art city  a ruling passion documentary   art in the twentyfirst century tv series documentary himself  consumption   himself getting started  contributor zone » contribute to this page edit page add resume get caught up on comiccon catch up with everything you missed at comiccon with imdbs  comiccon guide what liam cunningham liberated from the game of thrones set seth rogen talks about awards buzz for disaster artist browse our guide to comiccon   imdb everywhere find showtimes watch trailers browse photos track your watchlist and rate your favorite movies and tv shows on your phone or tablet imdb mobile site follow imdb on home top rated movies box office tv coming soon site index search in theaters contact us register news press room advertising jobs imdbpro box office mojo withoutabox conditions of use privacy policy interestbased ads copyright   imdbcom inc an amazoncom company amazon affiliates amazon video watch movies tv online prime video unlim